 Project structure
- alembic: directory with alembic setup
- app: application packages directory
- tests: app testing modules
- app/services: Service classes and utils that implements business logic
- app/cex: connectors to fetch data from CEX and orcestrators to optimize data operations
- app/web: web application
- app/market: extrnal market sources
- app/settings: app settings

